::Shredder::

Shredder growls as he recieves Quickstrike's transmission. Megatron had 
promoted him? He growls again. In his view, Quickstrike was a useless fuzor 
who kept being blown to crap, but then Shredder had bad opinions about 
everyone.

He shruggs. He'd talk to Megatron about it later.

"Very well," he says into his comm-link, "I'll get you your stasis pod."

Shredder walks off into the forest.
